  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6506363">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6506363/" class="title-link">献给生命和力量，献给家、族、国</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6506363"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/66139909/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u66139909-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/66139909/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">毛毛</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-01-13"
      class="main-meta">2014-01-13 09:06:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6506363_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         瞻对，是一个不易融化的铁疙瘩。而历史，是我一直没有融化的铁疙瘩。对于一个历史是硬伤的人来说，《瞻对》对我最大的吸引力莫过于藏地的传奇。而且有《尘埃落定》的阿来这个名字作为保障，这个瞻对的故事一定不会差。        藏地，以往在我的印象中，那里有对于生命的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6506363/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">13有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6506363_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6506363_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6491876">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6491876/" class="title-link">心生悲凉——隐在《瞻对》身后的告白</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6491876"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2338908/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2338908-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2338908/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">水秀乡</span>
